    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit boasts a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension has been optimized with polyurethane bushings and adjustable dampers for neutral handling characteristics. While the finish displays minor road-wear consistent with its driver-focused history, the engine compression remains within factory spec across all six cylinders and the individual throttle body (ITB) synchronization is precise. A true enthusiast's example prioritized for tactile feedback and longitudinal performance.",
