    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition, reflecting years of attentive ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment that feels remarkably fresh; the leather upholstery remains supple, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It comes with a comprehensive service log, featuring a recent major interval service and a fresh set of premium all-season tires. The engine starts promptly and idles smoothly, while the transmission provides crisp, confident shifts. This is a turn-key example that strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a vehicle you'll be proud to park in your driveway. It\u2019s ready for its next chapter with a buyer who appreciates a car that has been genuinely pampered.",
